columns.name: MAILOUOA2AC
columns.description:
To store the Outlook OAuth2 info related with SMTP IMAP and POP3
It is encrypted using the pattern we use for TConstants.FirebirdUsername
AccessToken

columns.name: MAILOUOA2RE
columns.description:
To store the Outlook OAuth2 info related with SMTP IMAP and POP3
It is encrypted using the pattern we use for TConstants.FirebirdUsername
RefreshToken

columns.name: MAILOUOA2REEX
columns.description:
To store the Outlook OAuth2 info related with SMTP IMAP and POP3
It is encrypted using the pattern we use for TConstants.FirebirdUsername
RefreshToken expiration, since we can not decrypt the data to get the real exp date, it is 85 days after getting the AccessToken
